              <tt>
               "&lt;x&gt; &lt;y&gt;"
              </tt>
              .
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              The elements in
              <b>
               design
              </b>
              will be unique.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               design
              </b>
              will describe a simple polygon containing only horizontal and vertical lines. No lines in the polygon will intersect or overlap other lines.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
