              </tt>
              in
              <b>
               design
              </b>
              and
              <b>
               connections
              </b>
              will be an integer between 0 and 1000, inclusive, and will not contain any leading zeros.
             </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
             <td align="center" class="statText" valign="top">
              -
             </td>
             <td class="statText">
              <b>
               hubs
              </b>
              will be between 1 and 20, inclusive.
             </td>
